{"title":"朝鲜谚语","authors":["朱瑞华"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":6,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理迟早必胜利。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了友谊故，头颅也可抛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"助人应及时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮人要诚心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结愈紧，力量愈大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力大的人并非都是勇士。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用扇扑不灭火焰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔朱瑞华辑译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}